early do you usually know?

00:03:48.040 --> 00:03:49.427
Is it a couple of days?

00:03:49.427 --> 00:03:51.010
Do they tell you
like the week before?

00:03:51.010 --> 00:03:53.184
And I'm like, literally
anywhere from like months

00:03:53.184 --> 00:03:54.350
to like a couple of minutes.

00:03:58.060 --> 00:04:02.330
Last week, I was playing
Uno with the other swings,

00:04:02.330 --> 00:04:03.580
and the stage manager came in.

00:04:03.580 --> 00:04:06.145
