be Jefferson in the second act.

00:04:06.145 --> 00:04:07.020
And that was just it.

00:04:07.020 --> 00:04:07.910
That's what happens.

00:04:07.910 --> 00:04:08.900
SPEAKER: So mid-show.

00:04:08.900 --> 00:04:09.010
JOSH ANDRÉS RIVERA: Yeah.

00:04:09.010 --> 00:04:09.565
Mid-show.

00:04:09.565 --> 00:04:11.440
And that's only happened
to me like a handful

00:04:11.440 --> 00:04:13.000
of times where that happens.

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:17.200
So honestly, originally,
that was really--

00:04:17.200 --> 00:04:19.810
I've never had to do
anything like that before.

00:04:19.810 --> 00:04:20.784
That was really hard.

00:04:20.784 --> 00:04:21.950
And it was really stressful.

00:04:21.950 --> 00:04:23.500
