thankful to be a part of it,

00:04:30.340 --> 00:04:32.950
but at the same time, there's
a gravity to it-- or there was.

00:04:32.950 --> 00:04:34.720
I mean, I don't so
much feel this anymore.

00:04:34.720 --> 00:04:36.470
I have relatively
gotten used to it.

00:04:36.470 --> 00:04:39.100
But at the beginning,
it was very

00:04:39.100 --> 00:04:44.350
crazy to have to just
be, yes, I'm enough.

00:04:44.350 --> 00:04:45.130
I can do it.

00:04:45.130 --> 00:04:47.770
You know?

00:04:47.770 --> 00:04:48.490
It's a lot.

00:04:48.490 --> 00:04:50.710
But I don't know.

00:04:50.710 --> 00:04:53.890
Now I really love it.

00:04:53.890 --> 00:04:56.289
You just never know what your
day is going to turn into.

00:04:56.289 --> 00:04:56.830
I don't know.

00:04:56.830 --> 00:04:58.560
It's so much fun for me.

00:04:58.560 --> 00:04:59.944
Especially because,
I don't know,

00:04:59.944 --> 00:05:01.360
I like to consider
myself somebody

00:05:01.360 --> 00:05:02.950
who goes with the flow.

00:05:02.950 --> 00:05:05.319
So it's just kind of like--

00:05:05.319 --> 00:05:05.860
I don't know.

00:05:05.860 --> 00:05:08.950
It's such a weird
thing to be able to do.

00:05:08.950 --> 00:05:10.791
I'm very proud of it now.

00:05:10.791 --> 00:05:11.290
Yeah.

00:05:11.290 --> 00:05:12.430
I don't know.

00:05:12.430 --> 00:05:15.750
I feel like I went in
a different direction.

